---
title: Scrambled Eggs and Cheesy Crumpets with Creamy Truffled Mushrooms
description: We love a good Scrambled Eggs & Crumpets & Mushrooms and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/scrambled-eggs-and-cheesy-crumpets-8b5a82b5-b81f5017.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/scrambled-eggs-and-cheesy-crumpets-5e87502a6fcecd78e41e3fbf-2ff634c9.pdf
servings: 2
